doc.previous: WikiProject Geographical coordinates aims to better organize location information in articles containing a set of numbers that identifies location on and relative to the Earth In particular we aim to establish a standard for uniform handling of latitude and longitude coordinates as given in various Wikipedia articles somewhat analogous to how ISBN numbers are handled
